---
title: Vegan Polenta Primavera with Bell Pepper, Zucchini, Mushrooms & Grape Tomatoes
description: A colorful mix of bell pepper, zucchini, mushrooms, and grape tomatoes simmers into a saucy veggie jumble, served over flavorful polenta enriched with nutty nutritional yeast. With precooked polenta and quick-sautéed vegetables, this comforting, plant-based dish comes together in no time.
